if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_orderaddress')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_orderaddress

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_orderaddress */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_orderaddress (
OAID int identity(1,1),
PackID int not null,
Name nvarchar(100) not null,
Address nvarchar(200) null,
Mobile nvarchar(50) null,
Phone nvarchar(50) null,
ZipCode nvarchar(20) null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
constraint PK_BUSI_ORDERADDRESS primary key (OAID)
)
go
